# Worker findings live here.
#
# One file per contribution, named <timestamp>-<agent>.md, e.g.
#   2026-01-01T1430-researcher.md
# Append-only: never overwrite another agent's entry.
#
# Each entry starts with frontmatter:
#   ---
#   agent: researcher
#   task: tasks/T3.md
#   status: done
#   summary: "<one line>"
#   ---
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the directory under version control while empty.
